            <entry xml:id="entry_iblis" xml:lang="os">
                <form type="lemma"><orth>iblis</orth><form type="variant"
                    ><orth>ibiliz</orth></form></form>
                <sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>дьявол</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>devil</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>демон</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>demon</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense></sense>
                <abv:exampleGrp>
                    <abv:example xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <usg><lang/></usg>
                        <quote>ibiliztæ, ʒintæ, æ sajtani xæjttæ…</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>иблисы, джины, его шайтановы доли…</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>iblises, djinns, his Satanic henchmen</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Bes._Ka_ke"
                            /><biblScope>21</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Из <mentioned xml:lang="ar"><lang/>
                        <w>iblīs</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>iblīs</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><lang/>
                        <w>iblis</w>
                        <gloss><q>дьявол</q></gloss></mentioned>. Вошло и в другие языки Кавказа:
                        <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><lang/>
                        <w>’iblis</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="av"><lang/>
                        <w>ilbis, iblis</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="lez"><lang/>
                        <w>iblis</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="x-vaynakh"><lang/>
                        <w>jilbaz, lilbaz</w></mentioned> и др. Ос. <ref type="xr"
                        target="#entry_fydbylyz"/> ‘беда’ (см. это слово) образовалось из <ref
                        type="xr" target="#entry_fyd"/>-%iiblis%i ‘злой демон’.</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">From <mentioned xml:lang="ar"><lang/>
                        <w>iblīs</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>iblīs</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><lang/>
                        <w>iblis</w>
                        <gloss><q>devil</q></gloss></mentioned>. Iy entered other languages of
                    Caucasus as well: <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><lang/>
                        <w>’iblis</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="av"><lang/>
                        <w>ilbis, iblis</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="lez"><lang/>
                        <w>iblis</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="x-vaynakh"><lang/>
                        <w>jilbaz, lilbaz</w></mentioned> etc. Ossetic <ref type="xr"
                        target="#entry_fydbylyz"/> ‘misfortune’ (see this word) was formed from <ref
                        type="xr" target="#entry_fyd"/>-%iiblis%i ‘evil demon’.</etym>
                <note type="internal">перевод примера!!</note>
            </entry>
